public class OsnOverviewEditor
extends oracle.bali.xml.gui.jdev.overviewEditor.AbstractOverviewEditor

Subclass of AbstractOverviewEditor that provides functionality for registering PanelWrapper factories, provides access to the standard toolbar, and responds to getHelpInfo requests.
